videos.description: On a handoff delay, Patrick Taylor is meets a wall of SMU defenders and goes down in the Memphis end zone for an SMU safety.
videos.headline: Taylor stuffed in the end zone for SMU safety

videos.description: Darrell Henderson finds a hole and erupts for a 35-yard gain and a Memphis first down.
videos.headline: Henderson bursts for a 35-yard gain

videos.description: Patrick Taylor Jr. takes the handoff, breaks one tackle then another to get in the end zone for a 9-yard touchdown and a Memphis 14-5 lead.
videos.headline: Taylor Jr. powers through tacklers for a TD

videos.description: Memphis QB Brady White's pass bounces out of the hands of his receiver and into the hands of SMU's Kevin Johnson for a 43-yard return.
videos.headline: SMU's Johnson returns INT for 43-yard gain

videos.description: SMU QB Ben Hicks connects with James Proche who catches and holds on to a 31-yard touchdown to cut the Memphis lead to 14-12.
videos.headline: Proche grabs and controls 31-yard TD

videos.description: Memphis Brady White finds and zips a 9-yard touchdown to Joey Magnifico for his second of the night and a 21-12 Memphis lead.
videos.headline: White rips 9-yard TD to Magnifico

videos.description: Patrick Taylor Jr. bursts for a 34-yard gain to set up a 1st-and-goal and later scores a 2-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Taylor's 34-yard run set up his 2-yard TD
